ered 7 p.m. @ 4°C 10/18/16 Purified by Isco LC   Standard Controls Apply: Lab coats, gloves and safety specs are to be worn at all times. All experiments should be performed in a fumehood. [AetherGen LIMS Verified]', '{"BOOK": "10", "ISID": "t.tra", "PAGE": "1", "DESCR": "Sonogashira coupling of Iodo-PRP with TMS acetylene", "STATUS": "0", "PROTOCOL": "ChemELN", "PROTOCOL_ID": "81", "CREATED_DATE": "13/10/2016", "PDF_COMPLETE": "Y", "COUNTERSIGNER": "chemist_052", "EXPERIMENT_ID": "138806", "MODIFIED_DATE": "31/10/2016", "COMPLETED_DATE": "26/10/2016", "COMPLETED_ISID": "t.tra", "CURRENT_VERSION": "1", "EXPERIMENT_NAME": "138806", "COUNTERSIGNED_DATE": "31/10/2016"}', '2025-01-30');
